92
00:07:48,843 --> 00:07:49,678
<i>¿Abuelo?</i>

93
00:07:49,678 --> 00:07:51,012


94
00:07:51,012 --> 00:07:52,347
<i>Perdóname, Yawara.</i>

95
00:07:52,347 --> 00:07:52,764


96
