No le des importancia. Ven.

147
00:11:05,165 --> 00:11:11,046


148
00:11:11,046 --> 00:11:12,714
Yawara, tú...

149
00:11:23,141 --> 00:11:24,059
¡Yawara!

150
00:11:28,438 --> 00:11:30,523
¡Espera, Yawara!

151
00:11:30,523 --> 00:11:30,815


152
00:11:34,027 --> 00:11:35,153
¿Qué te pasó en la mano?

153
00:11:36,196 --> 00:11:38,323
No tengo nada que decirte, Matsuda.


154
00:11:39,324 --> 00:11:42,118
No vine a entrevistarte.

155
00:11:42,827 --> 00:11:43,745
¿Ah, sí?

156
00:11:43,745 --> 00:11:44,329


157
00:11:44,329 --> 00:11:48,333
Créeme. Vine por razones personales.

158
00:11:48,333 --> 00:11:48,792


159
00:11:48,792 --> 00:11:52,837
Tenía la ligera sospecha de que
estarías tomando los exámenes de ingreso.

160
00:11:52,837 --> 00:11:53,296



161
00:11:53,296 --> 00:11:57,717
Apuesto que Kuni anda merodeando con su cámara.


162
00:11:57,717 --> 00:11:58,426


163
00:11:58,426 --> 00:11:59,761
No es así.

164
00:11:59,761 --> 00:12:01,137


165
00:12:01,137 --> 00:12:03,390
Buscas una exclusiva, ¿no es así?

166
00:12:03,723 --> 00:12:04,265
¡De ninguna manera!

167
00:12:04,599 --> 00:12:05,767
No puedo confiar en ti.

168
00:12:05,767 --> 00:12:05,850


169
00:12:05,850 --> 00:12:06,976
Créeme, por favor.

170
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:08,061
De ninguna manera.

171
00:12:08,144 --> 00:12:08,687
¡Por favor!

172
00:12:08,853 --> 00:12:12,399
