188
00:13:09,539 --> 00:13:10,665
Ya no puedo más.

189
00:13:10,665 --> 00:13:17,922


190
00:13:17,922 --> 00:13:18,548
Debo irme.

191
00:13:18,548 --> 00:13:19,382


192
00:13:19,382 --> 00:13:20,800
¿Vas a intentarlo con la mano así?

193
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:27,474


194
00:13:27,474 --> 00:13:28,099
Yawara.

195
00:13:29,893 --> 00:13:31,853
Estudié mucho para esto.

196
00:13:32,854 --> 00:13:34,856
