245
00:16:35,286 --> 00:16:36,329
¡Oh, no!

246
00:16:36,329 --> 00:16:37,288


247
00:16:37,288 --> 00:16:40,667
<i>Es imposible que haya podido</i>
<i>sostener el lápiz con esa lesión.</i>

248
00:16:40,667 --> 00:16:41,376


249
00:16:41,376 --> 00:16:43,253
